Make sure the following NuGet packages are installed in your project:

Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer
Used for database connections with SQL Server.

bash
Copy code
Install-Package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.SqlServer
Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Tools
Used for migrations and database management.

bash
Copy code
Install-Package Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Tools
Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity.EntityFrameworkCore
Provides Identity support for user management.

bash
Copy code
Install-Package Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity.EntityFrameworkCore
Rotativa.AspNetCore (Optional if PDF generation is planned later)
For generating PDF documents from Razor views.

bash
Copy code
Install-Package Rotativa.AspNetCore
